Our Aloo Paratha is a campus favorite — a golden, pan-roasted flatbread stuffed with a perfectly seasoned potato filling, straight from the Satish Hostel kitchen. Each paratha is made to order with love, ghee, and a pinch of hostel-style nostalgia.

Served piping hot with:

Homemade curd

Spicy pickle

Optional: Butter topping or extra ghee finish

💸 Budget-friendly. Flavor-rich. Always satisfying.

🔥 Pro tip: Add a chilled lassi for the ultimate combo!

Located in the heart of the city, the restaurant offers a rich culinary experience with a menu that celebrates the diversity of Indian flavors. From the spicy depths of Hyderabadi biryani to the delicate warmth of North Indian curries, every dish is crafted with traditional spices and home-style cooking. Whether you're in the mood for a hearty meal or a quick bite, Hotel Satish Biryani serves up delicious comfort food in a welcoming and casual setting. Perfect for families, food lovers, and anyone craving real Indian taste.
